# agent-device Fix Loop (automatic)

When the user asks to run the **fix loop**, **dogfood loop**, **test until green**, or **automatic QA loop**:

## Roles

| Tool | Job |
|------|-----|
| **agent-device + GitHub Actions** | Run Prodify on iOS Simulator, execute Maestro flow, capture screenshots/logs/video |
| **Cursor Agent (you)** | On failure: diagnose, fix code or flows, push, re-trigger CI |

agent-device does **not** edit the repo. You close the loop.

## Windows — no local Mac

Never run `agent-device` iOS commands locally on Windows. Use:

```powershell
.\scripts\run-agent-device-fix-loop.ps1 -FullApp -SkipSeed -Iteration <N>
```

## Loop algorithm (run autonomously until success or max 5 iterations)

```
iteration = 1
loop:
  run .\scripts\run-agent-device-fix-loop.ps1 -FullApp -SkipSeed -Iteration $iteration
  if exit 0 → read artifacts/qa-loop/latest/report.md, tell user success, show video path if any, STOP
  if exit 1 → read artifacts/qa-loop/latest/report.md
           → read failure.png + logs.txt from ci-artifacts
           → fix minimal change (mobile/ or mobile/maestro/flows/)
           → git commit + git push
           → iteration++, if iteration > 5 ask user; else goto loop
```

First iteration may omit `-SkipSeed` (script seeds on iteration 1 by default).

## Fix priorities

1. Maestro selector / timing / scroll (``mobile/maestro/flows/``)
2. React Native a11y labels matching ``mobile/locales/en.json``
3. App bugs only when logs/screenshots prove a real defect
4. Never enable production paywall in E2E — use ``EXPO_PUBLIC_E2E_MODE=true`` (already in CI)

## agent-device compatibility

- Do **not** use Maestro ``inputText: id:`` — use ``tapOn: "Email"`` then ``inputText``
- Prefer deep links: ``prodify://notifications``, ``prodify://progression-overview``, etc.

## Success deliverables

Tell the user:

- CI run URL
- Path to ``success.png`` and ``full-app-run.mp4`` (if full app flow)
- Short list of screens covered by ``full_app_test.yaml``

## User trigger phrases

- "Starte den agent-device Fix-Loop"
- "Teste und fixe bis alles grün ist"
- "Run the dogfood loop until green"
